00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:52.400 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:54.830 align:middle line:84%
>>HOWARD: And our
thoughts and our model

00:02:54.830 --> 00:02:57.300 align:middle line:84%
