They always say don't
try this at home--

00:19:19.080 --> 00:19:19.390 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:19:19.390 --> 00:19:19.950 align:middle line:84%
>>HOWARD: -but you
can try this at home.

00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:21.210 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Try this at home.

00:19:21.210 --> 00:19:23.340 align:middle line:84%
>>HOWARD: So first
of all, what is this?

