You're looking at the finger
vice suggestibility test.

00:19:26.621 --> 00:19:27.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:19:27.120 --> 00:19:27.786 align:middle line:90%
>>HOWARD: Right.

00:19:27.786 --> 00:19:30.310 align:middle line:84%
And so what a suggestibility
test is a teaching tool

00:19:30.310 --> 00:19:33.380 align:middle line:84%
to teach somebody how to
attain the depths of trance

00:19:33.380 --> 00:19:35.190 align:middle line:84%
where they could
actually give suggestions

00:19:35.190 --> 00:19:37.120 align:middle line:84%
to their unconscious mind
and their unconscious mind

00:19:37.120 --> 00:19:38.161 align:middle line:90%
follows through on those.

00:19:38.161 --> 00:19:39.370 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:19:39.370 --> 00:19:44.640 align:middle line:84%
>>HOWARD: And, you know,
the suggestibility test

00:19:44.640 --> 00:19:47.887 align:middle line:84%
allows you to build your belief
and expectation in hypnosis.

00:19:47.887 --> 00:19:49.470 align:middle line:84%
It does a lot of
other things as well,

00:19:49.470 --> 00:19:50.990 align:middle line:84%
but we'll just get
down to business here.

00:19:50.990 --> 00:19:51.270 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

