00:37:56.530 --> 00:37:57.740 align:middle line:90%
and how you go through it.

00:37:57.740 --> 00:38:00.030 align:middle line:84%
And, you know, the
world around us

00:38:00.030 --> 00:38:03.195 align:middle line:84%
